<br>
with every character I always have a definite order I put everything in, for my mage it goes as follows<br>
<br>
In Dungeons:<br>
<br>
1. Self Buff-Greater Sheilding (mostly for Magic Rez) or Elemental Sheild<br>
<br>
2. Big DD (Blaze at this point)<br>
<br>
3. Littler DD (24 DD for finishing of Runners)<br>
<br>
4. D-Sheild<br>
<br>
5. Gate (ALWAYS THERE)<br>
<br>
6. Nullify Magic (Usually saves tank some HP's on the MoBs D-sheilds, gets rid of Charms too)<br>
<br>
7. Burnout 2<br>
<br>
8. Whatever spell I used last, usually a summon spell or possibly pet Heal, Malise is also commonly there<br>
<br>
When out of dungeons pretty much the same order cept a Bolt Included (if higher dam than DD at time) and possibly an AE.<br>
