<br>
Some advice to the newbie Mages:<br>
Always keep gate up.<br>
Always have your pet spell up.<br>
Always have your fastest nuke loaded.<br>
Once you get Call of the Hero, keep it up as well, it has saved me and my party several times. When you get it speak to some Mages that have it as there are some pretty neat uses for the spell that might not be readily apparant. Good luck!<br>
